CLIPS> (defglobal ?*Answer* = nil)  ;creating a global variable to hold the user's answer
CLIPS> (defrule gadget_list
         (printout t "GADGETS AVAILABLE IN THE SYSTEM" crlf)
         (gadget ?name) 
        =>
         (printout t ?name crlf)) ;print out list of gadgets available in the system 
CLIPS> (rules) ;checking whether the rule has been created successfully
gadget_list
For a total of 1 defrule.

CLIPS> (defrule user_data
      (printout t "Please enter the name of the gadget you would like to know more about" )
     =>
 (bind ?*Answer* (read)))
CLIPS> (rules) ;checking if new rule(user_data) has been added
gadget_list
user_data
For a total of 2 defrules.
